<h2>Labs</h2>
<p></p>
These prototypes are for learning new software tools and techniques.  They are not feature-complete.<br/>
Let Andy know if you spot problems or have ideas for improvement.
<p></p>
<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Events</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td width=500>
      Time-tracking and coordination for BAMRU Events (meetings, trainings, operations).<br/>
      - Event data is LIVE!  Edit with care.<br/>
      - This feature works on Chrome / Firefox / Safari.<br/>
      - It works on IE after you install the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.google.com/chromeframe">ChromeFrame</a> plugin.
    </td>
    <td  valign='middle' style='padding-left: 40px;'>
      <%= link_to events_url, '/events'  %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Guests</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td width=500>
      Search/browse/sort the BAMRU guest list.<p></p>
    </td>
    <td  valign='middle' style='padding-left: 40px;'>
      <%= link_to guests_url, guests_path  %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p></p>
<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Mobile</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td width=500>
      BAMRU Mobile is a small and fast interface that runs in a mobile browser.<br/>
      It is designed for Android, iPhone, iPad, iPod, and also works on Chrome/Firefox.<br/>
    </td>
    <td valign='middle' style='padding-left: 40px;'>
      <span style="margin-right: 30px;"> <%= link_to mobile_url, mobile_path %></span>
      <%= raw qr_tag(mobile_url) %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p></p>
<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Messaging</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td width=500>
      Experiments with chat and real-time message feeds.<br/>
      The monitor shows a streaming activity log.
    </td>
    <td  valign='middle' style='padding-left: 40px;'>
      <%= link_to monitor_url, '/monitor'  %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p></p>
<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Meeting Sign In</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td width=500>
      Raw mockup for a Meeting Sign In app.  Runs on Smartphones & iPad.<br/>
      Registers Members & new Guests. Takes a profile photo.<br/>
    </td>
    <td valign='middle' style='padding-left: 40px;'>
      <%= link_to meeting_signin_url, meeting_signin_path %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

